{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0eda686cbf","title":"吉林省“三反”运动初步总结提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"028603e05b","index":0,"year":1952,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"0eda686cbf"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0425cde272","type":"title","text":"吉林省“三反”运动初步总结提纲","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"906143993e","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、总的要求","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"7b81b2908c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、总的要求是为了抓到450只大老虎，2000只小老虎而战。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"6f563b20af","type":"paragraph","text":"二、为打退资产阶级进攻，特别是占全省资本家5%的反动户（约1200家）。并彻底解决其中木材、营建、五金电料器材、代理店、银楼业、花纱加工、粮米油加工等行业的问题，明确今后对他们的具体政策。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"4f3449a871","type":"paragraph","text":"在此中要捉到800只以上的巨虎，分别予以处理。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"79b829544c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、经过这一运动，将大大提高吉林党的纯洁性，大约要从党内清洗出2000名钻进来、拉过去的分子。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"e58090bb4e","type":"paragraph","text":"四、要在这次运动中，运动后，大量提拔政治、思想纯洁，手脚干净，积极斗争，有一定业务能力的干部到各领导岗位上来，全省将提拔2500余人。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"dab29188a5","type":"paragraph","text":"五、要在这一运动中及运动后，打下坚固的思想教育的基础，业已证明并要继续证明给全省共产党员、青年团员看：共产主义的教育，毛泽东思想的教育，在今后全体同志中该用最大的决心去系统进行。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"7ff1a9cad1","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、现在进行的程度及情况","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"8e45eff212","type":"paragraph","text":"一、届至2月底止，全省将可抓到大老虎近200只，小老虎700只(2月20日统计是大老虎世  ①。小老虎  只②)。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"5e5d040b5b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、届二月底止全省可解决大部安定守法半守法的资本家做到退出漏税。可捕捉300余户，处理   户，五反斗争将解决一半左右。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"795330e174","type":"paragraph","text":"一、省直及吉、长两市的直属单位抓虎进度可分四种类型：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"9a2437f7e7","type":"paragraph","text":"第一种：大体捕到，尚需向纵深发展。（这种单位约占十分之一、二，人员比例则较更少）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"53ed60a34f","type":"paragraph","text":"第二种：达到一半，或接近任务之一半。（这种单位约占十分之四、五，但人员比例则更大于此。系较普遍的类型。）","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"092ff7f435","type":"paragraph","text":"第三种：进展很少，尚未突开全局。（这种单位约占十分之二、三，人员的比例大致于此相符合）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"3e8a4c6405","type":"paragraph","text":"第四种：没有进展，领导右倾，打虎僵持，需根本解决。（这种单位约占十分之一以下。人员员比例小于此）。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"c80d7afdb8","type":"paragraph","text":"附：区别的根据在于：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"1cab4b87bd","type":"paragraph","text":"①看这单位钱财吞吐；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"a69b9deb3f","type":"paragraph","text":"②业务范围；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"4517d71255","type":"paragraph","text":"③平日对干部的了解；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"c760654f0a","type":"paragraph","text":"④特别是执行打虎的战果；","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"9c9cc79158","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤没有绝对的藏虎的死角，死角已找到。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"d509f28a14","type":"paragraph","text":"二附：在省直来说：","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"2e7fd60e9f","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类如：人事厅、文教厅、民政厅、优抚处、财政厅厅内。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"2ab9bb1586","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类如：森工局、煤建公司、铁路、工程公司。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"ea680ea5ec","type":"paragraph","text":"第三类如：工业厅、及一部大厂矿。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"3604da6746","type":"paragraph","text":"第四类如：工业器材公司。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"b04b2d7f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、各县按蛟河为例（东北局及省检查组亲自去搞），一县一区的经验，已抓到大小老虎80只。大的3只、中等5只。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"a28d79e7c2","type":"paragraph","text":"按磐石、九台、桦甸等县运动已开展起来的地方看，这个数目是合于事实，较大的县将均可达到这个目标左右。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"a720ced0cc","type":"paragraph","text":"这样按平均数50只计算，将可抓到1300只老虎，大虎80余只。（现已抓到大虎  只，小虎  只）","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"3f57417152","type":"paragraph","text":"五、现在各县近况：届今日(21日)止，可分四种：.（1）很少动，不准备再大动的有永吉、怀德、长春、农安、长岭五县。（2）已动，但动的不深，如德惠、伊通、双阳、珲春、和龙、汪清、安图、郭前旗、乾安等县。（3）动的已深，但基本上尚可自己作战，动下去的，有磐石、舒兰、桦甸、延边地直延吉，但需派人通风报信（已派了两个小组）（4）动的已深，但领导上有问题，已发现严重大案可必需派人去掌握，不等要出偏差，有敦化、九台、榆树。蚊河（已有人，但仍要人做善后工作）","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"4013612d5b","type":"paragraph","text":"除未动及动后之后的14县不算。已动的九县，现已达到运动的1/3的进度有4县，1/4的有5县。第4种县必需即派人去领导。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"514a82fc73","type":"paragraph","text":"六、就全局来看，全省2月份打虎斗争是完成一半以上。另一半要在3月去完成。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"02ca5509be","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、如何布署？及力量问题。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"0f417d3794","type":"paragraph","text":"一、3月将是由定月，但现在有几个矛盾：①农村春耕，迫近备耕、购粮，5县委去人帮助。②省直运动还要3月去做。③长春需调大力去帮助。④新区的骨干抽不出来。⑤大问题更在力量不够。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"2012925486","type":"paragraph","text":"二、力量问题是决定关键","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"94b190384a","type":"paragraph","text":"全省干部26000人。可用之骨干约4000余人。（即区书以上的条件）现在分布：①半老区用800余人。省投入400，本地400余。②省直三反用千余人。③帮助吉市600人，可称骨干者200余人。④长、吉两市、延边地委、半老区、七县已搞三反，九县均无兵可调。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"b30379a3c0","type":"paragraph","text":"现在力量的问题是必需再集中800人。分配到长春500，厂矿及九县300。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"aedf079419","type":"paragraph","text":"但必需在3月中旬后，吉市可调出200，新区回来后经过洗澡可调300。（时间晚一些）","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"9f91b33b83","type":"paragraph","text":"一、三月布署，（按计划要求）","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"dc552dabda","type":"paragraph","text":"省直到3月20日，必需完成大虎250，小虎900。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"e41bb06da8","type":"paragraph","text":"长春必需同时完成大虎80小虎200。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"b1b79145c8","type":"paragraph","text":"吉市必须完成大虎40，小虎100。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"f0d2e9c7e2","type":"paragraph","text":"一专区、九县必需完成大虎40，小虎400。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"c4d0ce3a7a","type":"paragraph","text":"布署：2月10日后，某些500人到长春，各县帮助。其中三县2月末即派小组去。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"1d86276849","type":"paragraph","text":"第四、两个步骤","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"7c1b84013a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、反右倾。（见材料）","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"43eb9875ba","type":"paragraph","text":"二、公审大会准备。（见材料）","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"f3d9925cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"第五、几个请考虑指示的问题。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"99ce76ff1d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、计算老虎的标准。（也即是政策问题）","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"b1cac411f1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、贪污犯处理及例理时间问题。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"6779066f96","type":"paragraph","text":"三、省、市财经制度问题。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"2f5209e6c4","type":"paragraph","text":"四、干部提拔及管理制度问题。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"8030aedc88","type":"paragraph","text":"五、几个专案的处理问题。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"f032a3daa7","type":"paragraph","text":"注：此件转自省档案馆、省委宣传部1952年第3卷。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"d6f20e3c4e","type":"paragraph","text":"1952年   月③","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"},{"id":"0da6bc7d81","type":"paragraph","text":"编者注：①②③原文空缺。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf"}],"page":{"id":"4fe61bedcf","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0eda686cbf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}